<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Login | Wisuda Polinela</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logopolinela.png" type="image/png">

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-blue: #0047AB;
      --secondary-gold: #FFD700;
    }

    body, html {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Layout Split Screen */
    .login-container {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* --- SISI KIRI (VIDEO PLAYLIST) --- */
    .left-pane {
      position: relative;
      background-color: #002a6b;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Container untuk video agar menumpuk */
    .video-wrapper {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-video {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -30%;
      width: 140%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
      opacity: 0; /* Default tersembunyi */
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-video.active {
      opacity: 1; /* Muncul */
      z-index: 2; /* Di atas */
    }

    .video-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0, 71, 171, 0.95) 0%, rgba(0, 71, 171, 0.4) 50%, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 100%);
      z-index: 3; /* Di atas video */
    }

    .brand-content {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8%;
      left: 10%;
      right: 10%;
      z-index: 4;
      color: white;
    }

    .brand-content h1 {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .brand-content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    /* --- SISI KANAN (FORM) --- */
    .right-pane {
      background: #ffffff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem 6rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn-back {
      position: absolute;
      top: 2rem;
      left: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #6c757d;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .btn-back:hover {
      background-color: #e9ecef;
      color: var(--primary-blue);
      transform: translateX(-3px);
    }

    .form-header { margin-bottom: 3rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .logo-img { width: 60px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .welcome-title { font-weight: 700; color: #333; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    
    .form-control {
      padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 2px solid #f0f2f5;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .form-control:focus {
      background: #fff;
      border-color: var(--primary-blue);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 71, 171, 0.1);
    }
    
    .input-group-text {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border: 2px solid #f0f2f5;
      border-right: none;
      border-radius: 12px 0 0 12px;
      color: #888;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary-blue);
      border: none;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #003380;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 71, 171, 0.3);
    }

    .forgot-link { color: var(--primary-blue); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .register-link a { color: var(--primary-blue); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
    .alert { border-radius: 12px; border: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .alert-danger { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
    
    .shake { animation: shake 0.5s cubic-bezier(.36,.07,.19,.97) both; }
    @keyframes shake {
      10%, 90% { transform: translate3d(-1px, 0, 0); }
      20%, 80% { transform: translate3d(2px, 0, 0); }
      30%, 50%, 70% { transform: translate3d(-4px, 0, 0); }
      40%, 60% { transform: translate3d(4px, 0, 0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .left-pane { display: none; }
      .right-pane { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
      .btn-back { top: 1.5rem; left: 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container-fluid p-0 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="row g-0 login-container">
    
    <div class="col-lg-7 left-pane d-none d-lg-block">
      
      <div class="video-wrapper">
        <video id="player1" class="hero-video active" muted playsinline></video>
        <video id="player2" class="hero-video" muted playsinline></video>
      </div>
      
      <div class="video-overlay"></div>
      
      <div class="brand-content">
        <h1>Momen Puncak<br><span style="color: var(--secondary-gold);">Kebanggaan.</span></h1>
        <p>Satu langkah lagi menuju perayaan kelulusan Anda. Persiapkan diri untuk masa depan yang gemilang bersama Polinela.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-5 right-pane">
      <a href="/" class="btn-back"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i> Beranda</a>

      <div class="w-100" style="max-width: 480px;">
        <div class="form-header">
          <img src="/images/logopolinela.png" alt="Logo" class="logo-img">
          <h2 class="welcome-title">Selamat Datang ðŸ‘‹</h2>
          <p class="text-muted">Masuk ke Aplikasi Pendaftaran Wisuda</p>
        </div>

        <div id="loginAlert" class="alert d-none"></div>

        <form id="loginForm">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label class="form-label">Email Mahasiswa</label>
            <div class="input-group">
              <span class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></span>
              <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control border-start-0 ps-2" placeholder="Masukan Email yang Sesuai" required>
